<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7072] Multiple mlt.fl does not work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7072</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I tested the mlt component in Solr Admin query with this parameter&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mlt.fl=categories,tags,vtext
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It works.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;HOWEVER&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mlt.fl=categories&amp;amp;mlt.fl=tags&amp;amp;mlt.fl=vtext
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Does not work!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MOREOVER&lt;br/&gt;
The solrJ client seems to turn this line&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;query.setParam( &quot;mlt.fl&quot;, &quot;categories&quot;, &quot;tags&quot;, &quot;vtext&quot; );
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;into this&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mlt.fl=categories&amp;amp;mlt.fl=tags&amp;amp;mlt.fl=vtext
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Which, of course, does not work&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Win7 64bit/JDK8&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
